    "asOf": "2024-04-18",
    "date": "2024-10-17T18:51:05Z",
    "text": "Making Pipelines Accountable to Consumers and Taxpayers Act or the MPACT Act\n\nThis bill gives\u00a0the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission (FERC) the authority to order natural gas companies to pay refunds with interest to their consumers for rates or charges that are unjust, unreasonable, unduly discriminatory, or preferential. FERC must also establish refund effective dates as specified by the bill.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0"
